sourcesContent: import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-leadership', templateUrl: './leadership.component.html', styleUrls: ['./leadership.component.scss'] }) export class LeadershipComponent implements OnInit { imgTitle = './../../../assets/img/module-leadership.jpg' constructor( private router: Router, ) { } ngOnInit(): void { } goToAbout() { this.router.navigate(['about']) } }
